new Factorial:
    @ >> n.
    "n is " >+> (n >> Str) >> Display.
    n >> check:
        is <= 1: 1.
        else:
            n - 1 >> Factorial >> prev.
            "n is " >+> (n >> Str) >+> ", prev is " >+> (prev >> Str) >> Display.
            n * prev.
    ..
..

5 >> Factorial >> f5.
"5! = " >> out1.
(f5 >> Str) >+> out1 >> Display.
